<http://www.spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/event/12801AHKJCDVHRVVMMTDLCVKNKBDKHMLM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CapU Instrumental: Nocturnal Harmonies";
  schema:description """
	Step into a world where music and visuals intertwine. Directed by Dr. Rick Dorfer, \"Nocturnal Harmonies” invites audience members to experience the CapU Instrumental Ensemble like never before with immaculately performed melodies illuminated by captivating visual projections created by the musicians.<span><br/></span>Featuring works spanning Rachmaninoff to Led Zeppelin, this special show also features an exquisite premiere by CapU student Harshdeep Johal. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://capilanoumusic.ca/events\">CapU Music Website</a>
""";
