  schema:description """
	<h2>Capilano University is pleased to host the <span class=\"BoldText\">COWFLOP Spring 2026 Conference</span> at CapU Lonsdale Campus in North Vancouver<span class=\"ItalicText\">,</span> BC. </h2><span><br/></span>For information about this conference organized by the Council of Western Canadian Financial, Logistical, and Operational Personnel (COWFLOP), please email <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"mailto:angelaruggles@capilanou.ca\">Angela Ruggles</a>, Executive Assistant to Tally Bains, VP Finance and Administration.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Sales close April 14th 2026.<span><br/></span>
""";
